            "description": "When all the planets and the Lagna are in the Fixed signs like Taurus, Leo, Scorpio and Aquarius, a Musala yoga is the end result. Those with this yoga tend to be very straight forward about their ethos and principles in life. Administrative jobs are an excellent career choice for such people. Fame and prestigious achievements are likely to follow such people as a reward for their diligence. However such individuals don't roll well with change. Flexibility is definitely not their forte."
