            "name": "Raja Yoga",
            "description": "A typical Raja Yoga happens when two or more than two planets (out of which atleast one should be the lord of 'Kendra' & the other should be the lord of 'Trikon') is in a relationship with each other. This relationship can be a combination, bidirectional vision or exchange of zodiacs. A person with a Raja Yoga enjoys social status and fame.  Recognition and laurels will follow them for their efforts on various matters. In this chart there is relationship between Venus and Ketu planets."
